<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4535028>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 16. — A-C, Ramiporalia robusta Delvolve & McKinney, 1983; A, shallow tangential section showing autozooecial aperture, SMF 21.839; B, C, branch midtangential section, SMF 21.841; D-H, Tabulipora howsii (Nicholson, 1881); D, E, tangential section showing autozooecial apertures and acanthostyles (arrow), SMF 21.852; F, H, longitudinal section showing ring septa, SMF 21.851. Scale bars: A, H, 0.2 mm; B, C, F, G, 1 mm; D, E, 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4535028/files/figure.png" .

